# Product Scope Guardrails

Never add these in MVP:
- Payment processing
- Direct checkout
- Instant booking confirmation
- Full admin CRM/dashboard suite

Always enforce:
- Booking Assistant creates request only
- Gift Constructor redirects to Shopify or captures lead
- Consent is required on each form
- Public text is multilingual-ready (`en`, `it`, optional `ru`)
